==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perique
<hw>Pe*rique"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Louisiana F.]</ety>
<def>A kind of tobacco with medium-sized leaf, small stem, tough and
gummy fiber, raised in Louisiana, and cured in its own juices, so as to
be very dark colored, usually black. It is marketed in tightly wrapped
rolls called carottes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

